@notifications - all notifications for this user.
@email - users email

to create a path to unsubscribe:
unsubscribe_product_path(Notification.get_remove_hash(email, notification.product)
this link will unsubscribe only one product. So if email is sent with notification about 3 products you will have to generate appropriate number of unsubscribe links. This prevents user to get many emails from you about product changes.
